```

This appears to be a truncated line that references `R.drawable.trophy`, but the R class isn't being imported or resolved properly. Looking at the current file, I can see on line 276 there's:

```kotlin
icon = { Icon(painter = painterResource(R.drawable.trophy), contentDescription = "Trophy") },
